  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*1-site)\n<0| - I'll give you my vacuum\n|Ψ>\n<0|Ψ> = 1.\nQs, Q1,Q2,Q12\n(f[u])[1-site su(2) Gaudin] = ∫ du μ[u] f[u]\n",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "brG[f_]:=Residue[f/u^2,{u,0}];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
